==English==

===Etymology===
From Old English

===Pronunciation===
/pæn/

===Noun===
'''pan''', plural '''[[pans]]'''
# Flat [[implement]] used for cooking in the oven and [[fry]]ing or [[boil]]ing on top of the stove.
# [[load|Loaf]] of [[bread]].

