===Transitive verb===
'''pan''', '''[[pans]]''', '''[[panning]]''', '''[[panned]]'''
# [[disparage]], belittle, put down, minimize the importance of
#: ''The critics really '''panned''' that movie.''

===Etymology===
From the Greek word meaning ''all''.

===Intransitive verb===
'''pan''', '''[[pans]]''', '''[[panning]]''', '''[[panned]]'''
# To move a [[movie camera]] [[sideways]].

